{!<p class="other">!}[? if year = 1931 and month = 4 and PLR_launched : The collection of signatures for the proposed Prussian Landtag referendum has ended, with [+ landtag_ref_signatures +]% voting in favor of the petition. [? if landtag_ref_signatures < 20: Therefore, with a 20% quota, the petition has failed. This is a small victory for the survival of our democracy, and has demoralized and wasted the funds of the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">far</span>-<span style="color: #3E88B3;">right</span>. ?][? if landtag_ref_signatures >= 20: Therefore, with a 20% quota, the petition has passed. This is unexpected, and now we urgently need to step up our propaganda game, to rival the storm from the <span style="color: #3E88B3;">right</span>. The plebiscite is set to be voted on this August.?] ?]{!</p>!}

